t/_/rihanna/ | title=Rihanna | publisher=[[Official Charts Company]] | accessdate=October 29, 2012 | format=select \"Albums\" tab}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:90%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br /><ref name=\"US-albums\">{{cite web | url=https://www.billboard.com/music/rihanna/chart-history/billboard-200 | title=Rihanna \u2013 Chart History: Billboard 200 | work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]| accessdate=September 9, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Music of the Sun]]''\n|\n* Released: August 12, 2005 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web | url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/music-of-the-sun/id79555792 | title=Music of the Sun by Rihanna | work=[[iTunes Store]] | accessdate=October 27, 2012 | url-status=dead | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120507031535/http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/music-of-the-sun/id79555792 | archivedate=May 7, 2012 | df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n* Label: [[Def Jam Recordings|Def Jam]], SRP\n* Formats: [[Compact disc|CD]], CD/[[DVD]], [[Gramophone record|LP]], [[music download|digital download]]\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || 7 || 93 || 31 || 12 || 26 || 38 || 35 || 10\n|\n* UK: 148,660{{efn|name=UK1 sales|United Kingdom sales figures for ''Music of the Sun'', ''A Girl like Me'', ''Good Girl Gone Bad'' and ''Rated R'' as of November 2012.<ref name=\"Music Week sales\">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicweek.com/analysis/read/official-albums-chart-analysis-rihanna-becomes-first-ever-caribbean-artist-with-4-no-1s/052679|title=Official Albums Chart Analysis: Rihanna becomes first-ever Caribbean artist with 4 No.1s|last=Jones|first=Alan|date=November 26, 2012|work=[[Music Week]]|accessdate=June 9, 2015}}</ref>}}\n* [[Nielsen SoundScan|US]]: 623,000{{efn|name=US album sales June 2015|United States sales figures for all the studio albums as of June 2015.<ref name=\"US Album Sales\">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6605708/ask-billboard-rihannas-best-selling-songs-albums |title=Ask Billboard: Rihanna's Best-Selling Songs & Albums |last=Trust |first=Gary |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |date=June 23, 2015 |accessdate=June 23, 2015}}</ref>}}\n* WW: 2,000,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.biography.com/people/rihanna-201257|title=Rihanna - Biography - Singer|work=[[People (magazine)|People]]|accessdate=April 22, 2015}}</ref>\n|\n* [[Recording Industry Association of America|RIAA]]: Gold<ref name=\"RIAA\">{{cite certification|region=United States|artist=Rihanna|accessdate=January 27, 2016}}</ref>\n* [[British Phonographic Industry|BPI]]: Gold<ref name=\"BPI\">{{cite certification|region=United Kingdom|artist=Rihanna|accessdate=January 27, 2016}}</ref>\n* [[Bundesverband Musikindustrie|BVMI]]: Gold<ref name=\"BVMI\">{{cite web|url=https://www.musikindustrie.de/markt-bestseller/gold-/platin-und-diamond-auszeichnung/datenbank/?action=suche&strInterpret=Rihanna&strTtArt=alle&strAwards=checked|title=Gold-/Platin-Datenbank|accessdate=November 28, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Music Canada|MC]]: Platinum<ref name=\"MC\">{{cite certification | region=Canada | artist=Rihanna | accessdate=October 29, 2012}}</ref>\n* [[Recorded Music NZ|RMNZ]]: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.radioscope.net.nz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=79&Itemid=62 |title=Lates Gold / Platinum Albums |publisher=Radioscope New Zealand |accessdate=March 18, 2015 |url-status=unfit |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724195817/http://www.radioscope.net.nz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=79&Itemid=62 |archivedate=July 24, 2011 }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[A Girl like Me (Rihanna album)|A Girl like Me]]''\n|\n* Released: April 11, 2006 {{small|(US)}}<ref>{{cite web | url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/a-girl-like-me/id171762971 | title=A Girl Like Me by Rihanna | work=[[iTunes Store]] | accessdate=October 27, 2012}}</ref>\n* Label: Def Jam, SRP\n* Formats: CD, LP, digital download\n| 9 || 10 || 1 || 18 || 13 || 5 || 7 || 6 || 5 || 5\n|\n* UK: 667,672{{efn|name=UK1 sales